issue.title: feature request: `--redo` flag
issue.body:
Often, I find myself doing 
```sh
git cc -m "feat: ..." 
echo "pre-commit hooks rejected my commit"
# make fixes
git commit -m "$(cat ./.git/COMMIT_EDITMSG)"
```

It would be nice to encode this workflow as `git cc --redo`
